===Adverb===
{{Unicode|'''þā'''}}
# [[then]]
#:''Her comon ærest þa VII scipu and gehergoden Hamtun'': then in this year first came 7 ships, and ravaged Southampton.  (''AS Chronicles'')

===Conjunction===
{{Unicode|'''þā'''}}
# [[when]], [[since]], [[because]], [[where]]
